description: Dynamic analysis of Korean cryptographic library usage showing SEED, ARIA, HIGHT, and other KISA-standardized algorithms
expected_analysis_points: Korean domestic algorithms (SEED, ARIA, HIGHT, LEA, KCDSA, EC-KCDSA, HAS-160, LSH)
library loading patterns and function call signatures
symmetric ciphers vulnerable to Grover's algorithm (AES-128, 3DES, DES, RC4)
